{
  "stem": "8784.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were daredevils by that time because I don't think we would have done it two years ago.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But by that time, we dared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- lo and behold, we got into the ladies' quarters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were no ladies there that I recall.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But we dropped off some of that food stuff.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We simply dropped that off, and we went off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But as we came out, there was a-- a woman SS guard standing at the-- at the same gate that was supposed to be before.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so now we were dying 100 deaths on what could happen to us.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But again, this was Schindler's camp, and the situation was not similar to other concentration camps, and nothing happened immediately.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But at the daily assembly-- at the Appelplatz-- and the assemblies there took place inside the factory hall, in a hall.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "At that-- in that evening, a-- the commandant or the SS commandant of that camp came forth and yelled out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I don't speak German, but certain things that were said at that time left such deep impressions that I cannot forget them.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And this commandant yelled out in German, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I couldn't say so many German words in my life as I all of a sudden remember.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that's exactly what he said.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what this means is, where are the two men that were in the ladies' barracks?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for a while, as it happens, the two of us who worked together as carpenters stood together.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And for a while, we hesitated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But again, this is 1945, Schindler's camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we hesitated for a while, but then we decided that we better step forward and-- and tell them who it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we step up and tell, we-- we're the one.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were in the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
